Grabówka  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Mikołajki, within Mrągowo County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  north-east of Mikołajki,  east of Mrągowo, and  east of the regional capital Olsztyn.
